data.title: Laser Photonics (NASDAQ: LASE) lands high six-figure robotic CleanTech order for AI data centers
data.description: Laser Photonics secures a high six-figure robotic laser cleaning workcell deal to process metal plates for AI data center equipment, aiming to boost assembly efficiency.
